description:
&lt;p&gt;We are a friendly GP practice in Watford looking to replace our Medical Secretary who is leaving. We are a busy surgery with 6Partners, 2 salaried GP&#39;s,an Advanced Nurse Practitioner, 2 nurses and a full team of receptionists and administrators.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position involves dealing with all our GP&#39;s and assisting them by typing their dictations and also putting through the electronic booking system for hospitals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Medical Secretary will deal with all aspects of patients records featuring mainly hospital referrals and dealing with patient queriessuch as referrals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our clinical System is Emis and whilst it is preferred to have experience of this, training can be provided as long as you have secretarial experience, are able to do audio typing and have adequate computer knowledge. &lt;/p&gt;
